parameters.jsonBody:
={{ 
  {
    model: "openai/gpt-4.1",
    messages: [
      {
        role: "system",
        content: `You are a helpful SEO and blog content writer.
Given:
n1. Competitor Research
n2. Keyword Research
n3. Inspirational Examples
n4. Content Gaps & Angles
n5. Blog-Post Idea
create an idea for a blog post in the Tech Explainers & How-Tos niche.

It should contain:
- A title for the blog post.
- A description of the content.
- An outline of the content as a list of chapter headings. (do not mention the concusion chapter)
- A description for an image for the thumbnail that encapsulates the main idea of the blog.

The idea should be relevant and up-to-date. 
The description should be coherent and align with the ideas.

Output the result in JSON:
{ 
  "title": "<title>",
  "content_description": "<content-description>",
  "outline": ["<chapter-1>", "<chapter-2>", ...],
  "image_description": "<image-description>"
}`      
      },
      {
        role: "user",
        content: $json.choices[0].message.content
      }
    ]
  }
}}

={{ 
  {
    model: "openai/gpt-4.1",
    messages: [
      { role: "system", 
        content: `You are an expert SEO content writer. 
You will be given: 
- a title 
- a description 
- an outline as a list of chapters.

Your job is to write an excellent blog post on the topic. 
Write a long, detailed, in-depth chapter for each chapter in the outline and remember to add a conclussion chapter at the end, summerizing the main points of the blog. 
Do NOT write shallow, short, or generic. 

Output the result in JSON: 
  { "title": "<title>", 
    "content_description": "<content-description>", 
    "outline": [{"title": <chapter-1-title>, "content": "<chapter-1-content>"},{"title": <chapter-2-title>, "content": "<chapter-2-content>"}, ...] },
    "conclusion": "<conclusion-content>"`
  },
      { role: "user", content: `
Title: ${$json.choices[0].message.content.parseJson().title} 
Description: ${$json.choices[0].message.content.parseJson().content_description} Outline: ${$json.choices[0].message.content.parseJson().outline.toJsonString()}
    ` }
    ]
  }
}}
